data.description: This fantastic home in Rose Nielson has all of the boxes checked! From the brick exterior to the spacious bedrooms to the large formal dining room, you couldn't ask for more! This classic home boasts of tons of built in storage, an indoor workshop, RV pad and A/C! The Master suite has a makeup area with a second sink, large walk in closet and is super roomy. There are 2 more huge bedrooms and a full bath with a jetted tub on this level. The main floor has a large kitchen with plenty of storage, a formal dining room, and a large living room with big windows. In the family room you will find a fabulous white brick fireplace with a gas insert (needs to be connected), big bedroom, and laundry with a 3/4 bath. Downstairs is a large workshop and another large family or craft room. The covered patio is oh my heavens fabulous to extend your living space. A quiet street in a great neighborhood with many bells and whistles. This home has a newer roof, updated windows and all the appliances stay! What a jewel! Come see this one before it's gone!
